GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 27th May 1964.
The undersigned is directed to state that
consequent on the sad demise of Shri Jawaharlal Nehru,
Prime Minister, the Council of Ministers stood dissolved
with effect from the afternoon of Wednesday, May 27, 1964.
2.
The Members of the new Council of Ministers named
in the enclosed list assumed office with effect from the
afternoon of Wednesday, May 27, 1964.
-10
